  "notes": {
    "psm": "UsddPsm allows 1:1 swaps between USDD and USDT. buyGem(usr, gemAmt) = spend USDD, receive USDT. sellGem(usr, gemAmt) = spend USDT, receive USDD. gemAmt is in USDT decimals (6). Fees (tin/tout) are currently 0.",
